casebody.data:
No. 586,

Misc.

Cicenia v. Lagay, Superintendent, New Jersey Prison Farm. Petitioner pro se. Charles V. Webb, Jr. and C. William Caruso for respondent.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit granted.

Mr. Justice Brennan took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
